  Added from_dict() classmethod to ChoiceDTO following the established pattern from other DTOs (TaskDTO, GoalDTO, UserDTO).

  The implementation:
  - Parses datetime fields (decision_deadline, created_at, updated_at, decided_at)
  - Ensures list fields are lists (not None)
  - Handles nested options list by converting dicts to ChoiceOptionDTO
  - Filters to only known fields to avoid unexpected kwargs
  - Returns properly typed ChoiceDTO instance
